---
---
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Personal Space — Juan Pablo Bascur</title>
    <style>
      * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        font-family: 'Georgia', serif;
        background: #1a1a1a;
        color: #f5f0e8;
        min-height: 100vh;
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem;
      }
      nav {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
        max-width: 680px;
        margin: 0 auto 4rem;
      }
      .nav-home {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #888;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      }
      .nav-home:hover { color: #f5f0e8; }
      .nav-switch {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #555;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        border: 1px solid #333;
        padding: 5px 14px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        transition: border-color 0.15s, color 0.15s;
      }
      .nav-switch:hover { border-color: #666; color: #f5f0e8; }
      .content { max-width: 680px; margin: 0 auto; }
      .label {
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #555;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
      }
      h1 {
        font-size: 48px;
        font-weight: 400;
        line-height: 1.2;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        color: #f5f0e8;
      }
      .intro {
        font-size: 17px;
        color: #aaa;
        line-height: 1.8;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
        max-width: 540px;
      }
      .section-title {
        font-size: 11px;
        letter-spacing: 0.15em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #444;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
      }
      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
        gap: 1px;
        background: #2a2a2a;
        border: 1px solid #2a2a2a;
        border-radius: 12px;
        overflow: hidden;
        margin-bottom: 4rem;
      }
      .card {
        background: #1a1a1a;
        padding: 1.5rem 1.25rem;
        text-decoration: none;
        color: inherit;
        display: block;
        transition: background 0.15s;
      }
      .card:hover { background: #222; }
      .card-title {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 400;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
        color: #f5f0e8;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      }
      .card-desc {
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.5;
        font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
      }
      .wip { color: #333; font-size: 11px; font-family: system-ui, sans-serif; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <nav>
      <a class="nav-home" href="/">jpbascur.com</a>
      <a class="nav-switch" href="/professional">→ professional space</a>
    </nav>

    <div class="content">
      <div class="label">Personal Space</div>
      <h1>The rest<br>of who I am</h1>
      <p class="intro">Beyond the resume — writing, projects I do for fun, things I think about, and whatever else ends up here.</p>

      <div class="section-title">Explore</div>
      <div class="grid">
        <a class="card" href="#">
          <div class="card-title">Software</div>
          <div class="card-desc wip">Coming soon</div>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="/writing">
          <div class="card-title">Creative writing</div>
          <div class="card-desc">Stories</div>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="#">
          <div class="card-title">Blog & essays</div>
          <div class="card-desc wip">Coming soon</div>
        </a>
        <a class="card" href="#">
          <div class="card-title">Hobbies</div>
          <div class="card-desc wip">Coming soon</div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
